rawContent:
I can hear and see so many people around me. Watching, waiting. Being visible is excruciating. 

What is it that I want?

What happened?

My mind is screaming "bring me back" but to when? 
Where could we possibly go that we know is safe?
I can't remember.

#depression #poetry
